version_description: Attention: We are currently experiencing issues with iOS 9 and later, which results in the in-game music not being played correctly. We are working on the issue, but in the meantime you can still play your own music in the background.

● Fixed music playback in iOS 9.
● Added support for 64-bit devices.
● Requires iOS 6 or later to play.
